Data model:

Credentials:
   username
   password

User:
  username = > pk
  name
  age
  photo
  status
  location

Posts:
  postID = > pk
  text
  mediaUrl
  parentPostID
  username
  timestamp
  

Friendships:
   friend1ID => fk for Users(username)
   friend2ID  => fk for Users(username)

PendingRequest:
  AcceptorID : user id of accepter
  SenderID: user id of initiater

Postmentions:
  postID
  mentionID: a user id


* user id and username is same.

Notifications:
   type: {birthday,post,reply}
   postID
   timestamp
   userid
   seen : true or false


RecommendedFriends:
  userid
  friendid

MaxIdTable:
  postidmax={ postidmax: } max value of postid in database



   


All these tables will be collections.


UI pages::
First page will be home where posts of all the friends of user will be displayed sorted by time.
Notifications page.
write post page.
find friends page.
friend requests page.
Create User page.


